---
description: Spec-Driven Development — 4-phase gated workflow for new features or ambiguous requirements. Manual rule; invoke when starting a feature.
---

Apply the spec-driven workflow documented at
`ai/skills/spec-driven/SKILL.md`. Load that file in full when this
rule is activated.

Phases: SPECIFY → PLAN → TASKS → IMPLEMENT. Human review at each
transition. Do not skip ahead.

When NOT to apply: typo fixes, unambiguous one-liners, bug fixes
whose root cause is already understood.
